PrecisApproval of an amendment to the VETERANS BURIAL REGULATIONS which requires that a claim for the reimbursement of funeral expenses must be made within one year after the death of the eligible veteran or pensioner, effective July 1, 1993.

precis:
Approval of an amendment to the VETERANS BURIAL REGULATIONS which requires
that a claim for the reimbursement of funeral expenses must be made within
one year after the death of the eligible veteran or pensioner, effective
July 1, 1993.
